body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Jackson Auto Sales. My name is Louis Jackson. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Samantha. Can you please provide me with the first three digits of your phone number and the last four digits of your social security number for verification purposes?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, the first three digits of my phone number are nine eight six and the last four digits of my social security number are three five zero zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Samantha. I have your information confirmed. How can I assist you with Jackson Auto Sales today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling confused about the privacy policy on your website.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand, Samantha. We take your privacy seriously. Our policy is designed to protect your personal information. Is there a specific section you have questions about?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm unsure about how my data is stored and who has access to it.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I can provide you with detailed information on our data storage practices and who can access your information. Would you like me to assist you with that now?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, please. That would be helpful.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your time and your questions, Samantha. If you have any more concerns, feel free to reach out. Have a great day.
